 like rhinovirus, but this is getting more complicated.","dimension":11,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.058424,0.10225,0.10134,0.10906,0.094715,0.088869,0.091471,0.080087,0.075295,0.080202,0.066344,0.051933],"unified_progress":[0.043542,0.079981,0.093349,0.10464,0.10172,0.095839,0.097584,0.091409,0.084875,0.086157,0.067606,0.053299]},{"section":6,"text":"The fever and the pus in the nose make me think it's not just a simple cold.","dimension":3,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.064666,0.086822,0.091247,0.094025,0.089647,0.087534,0.088552,0.084274,0.081442,0.082571,0.077731,0.071489],"unified_progress":[0.05616,0.077094,0.083843,0.089443,0.091578,0.091726,0.092595,0.093012,0.089083,0.087156,0.079373,0.068936]},{"section":7,"text":"The middle meatus is one of the sinuses, so maybe it's a sinus infection.","dimension":3,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.04704,0.068655,0.08501,0.098697,0.098835,0.099355,0.10067,0.095389,0.088674,0.084975,0.071926,0.060771],"unified_progress":[0.041706,0.068892,0.086654,0.097846,0.099884,0.10009,0.099825,0.096009,0.09339,0.086138,0.072369,0.0572]},{"section":8,"text":"Sinusitis can be acute or chronic.","dimension":2,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.03556,0.059756,0.077675,0.089834,0.097732,0.1016,0.10532,0.10311,0.098356,0.092742,0.0754,0.062908],"unified_progress":[0.036443,0.065392,0.084208,0.095596,0.09953,0.10595,0.10364,0.099955,0.094238,0.088135,0.071952,0.054956]},{"section":9,"text":"She's had a cold for 14 days, which could mean it's either acute","dimension":0,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.052968,0.085527,0.091132,0.089459,0.088314,0.088778,0.091222,0.089661,0.088623,0.08802,0.078714,0.067584],"unified_progress":[0.076887,0.098142,0.089852,0.086498,0.087461,0.088824,0.085766,0.089689,0.083455,0.078962,0.072169,0.062296]},{"section":10,"text":"or maybe it's turning chronic.","dimension":3,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progr