e after using topical decongestants, there was pus in the middle meatus.","dimension":10,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.070042,0.11305,0.11825,0.11154,0.10546,0.094336,0.087178,0.075559,0.067363,0.059055,0.052571,0.045595],"unified_progress":[0.069848,0.10447,0.10814,0.11033,0.10615,0.098317,0.088884,0.081761,0.079276,0.061971,0.051284,0.039572]},{"section":4,"text":"Hmm, so starting with the basics.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.35508,0.139,0.064641,0.064275,0.055986,0.077198,0.054115,0.052169,0.045956,0.040196,0.034302,0.017088],"unified_progress":[0.23017,0.092695,0.071808,0.067931,0.078387,0.072994,0.084394,0.07608,0.070225,0.055684,0.050457,0.049174]},{"section":5,"text":"A cold usually lasts about a week or two, but 14 days is on the longer side.","dimension":2,"group":7,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.112,0.14565,0.12342,0.10961,0.095528,0.080366,0.074567,0.065111,0.058149,0.051826,0.045333,0.03844],"unified_progress":[0.068125,0.10452,0.076673,0.10075,0.1041,0.096581,0.096778,0.087425,0.081028,0.073598,0.063365,0.04706]},{"section":6,"text":"But then she developed these new symptoms: fever, purulent discharge, facial pain, and a cough.","dimension":14,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.067629,0.12763,0.10886,0.079394,0.082911,0.077424,0.076346,0.075582,0.071983,0.063194,0.081396,0.087648],"unified_progress":[0.11602,0.15239,0.11333,0.096453,0.082515,0.081769,0.071258,0.077832,0.064179,0.057016,0.049089,0.038141]},{"section":7,"text":"The presence of pus in the middle meatus after decongestants makes me think of something more than a regular upper respiratory infection.","dimension":17,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.046383,0.082795,0.093326,0.10117,0.095775,0.09304,0.09211,0.088977,0.085478,0.080237,0.07389,0.066815],"unified_progress":[0.049037,0.080165,0.098639,0.10334,0.10203,0.09854,0.095137,0.089037,0.088257,0.07673,0.066024,0.053063]},{"section":8,"text":"I remember that sinusitis is an infection of the sinuses, often following a cold.","dimension":15,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.043,0.070564,0.082589,0.090708,0.096252,0.097643,0.10098,0.09936,0.093053,0.086874,0.074898,0.064077],"unified_progress":[0.042828,0.071838,0.089562,0.099534,0.10176,0.10631,0.10131,0.096351,0.090213,0.082716,0.066895,0.050682]},{"section":9,"text":"The sinuses can get blocked, leading to infection.","dimension":9,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.048007,0.066228,0.081001,0.090988,0.096279,0.098166,0.10131,0.099378,0.094418,0.086055,0.075195,0.06297],"unified_progress":[0.045365,0.070236,0.087161,0.097806,0.10232,0.1033,0.10073,0.097038,0.093297,0.083764,0.067909,0.051064]},{"section":10,"text":"The middle meatus is part of the sinuses, specifically the maxillary sinuses.","dimension":9,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.034108,0.066288,0.086667,0.10035,0.10618,0.10573,0.10745,0.098719,0.090892,0.077608,0.067701,0.058301],"unified_progress":[0.035493,0.072891,0.094993,0.10824,0.11291,0.10783,0.10284,0.093839,0.093765,0.072939,0.057791,0.046478]},{"section":11,"text":"So if there's pus there, that's a sign of infection.","dimension":17,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.034735,0.094474,0.11163,0.12014,0.10644,0.098275,0.09245,0.086049,0.077117,0.069478,0.059213,0.04999],"unified_progress":[0.029512,0.069336,0.090829,0.10421,0.10635,0.10484,0.10807,0.10008,0.092666,0.084771,0.065331,0.044002]},{"section":12,"text":"The symptoms she's presenting\u2014fever, purulent discharge, facial pain\u2014are classic for sinusitis.","dimension":14,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.048418,0.09784,0.093913,0.082877,0.083572,0.081689,0.081937,0.082902,0.080838,0.074092,0.091852,0.10007],"unified_progress":[0.094169,0.12739,0.10346,0.089256,0.086246,0.083674,0.078496,0.082142,0.07386,0.067466,0.061236,0.052601]},{"section":13,"text":"The fever suggests a bacter